===Etymology===
Cognate with {{term|坪|tr=tsubo|lang=ja}}.  Likely shares its origin with {{term|粒|tr=tsubu|lang=ja}}, in expressing the idea of something round and bulging outward.

===Noun===
{{ja-noun|k|hira=つぼ|rom=tsubo}}

# A [[container]] or depression:
## A [[pot]] or [[jar]]; a [[vessel]] or [[bottle]].
## A [[basin]], as at the base of a waterfall.
## A [[pressure point]] in [[acupressure]] or [[acupuncture]].
# The [[core]] or [[heart]] of an issue.

